1
00:01:24,359 --> 00:01:26,000
Sis, where are you?

2
00:01:26,319 --> 00:01:27,159
Big brother is here with Master Ning.

3
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:28,079
We've come to save you.

4
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:29,719
Imperial Inspectorate, official business!

5
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:31,439
Tell Hu Qiang to get out here!

6
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:35,560
Who dares cause such a racket?

7
00:01:36,079 --> 00:01:37,079
This is outrageous!

8
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:37,840
Master Ning.

9
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:39,200
He's Hu Qiang.

10
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:43,239
Who dares call me by name?

11
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:46,319
By the look of it, we're still in time.

12
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:49,480
Who are you?

13
00:01:49,959 --> 00:01:51,879
How dare you barge into the Hu residence?

14
00:01:52,719 --> 00:01:53,640
Where is Xiao Mei?

15
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:55,760
What Mei?

16
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:03,920
Where is Xiao Mei?

17
00:02:04,159 --> 00:02:04,879
Help!

18
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:05,840
I don't know.

19
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,280
I don't know where Xiao Mei is.

20
00:02:13,599 --> 00:02:14,599
I don't know!

21
00:02:20,319 --> 00:02:21,280
Still not talking, huh?

22
00:02:21,879 --> 00:02:22,560
Stop!

23
00:02:24,719 --> 00:02:25,199
You...

24
00:02:26,599 --> 00:02:27,199
Who are you?

25
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,280
I am Hu Maode.

26
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,199
Greetings, my lord.

27
00:02:32,719 --> 00:02:34,639
What crime has my son committed?

28
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:36,280
Take my advice.

29
00:02:36,919 --> 00:02:37,800
Have another son.

30
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,240
As for his life,

31
00:02:40,039 --> 00:02:40,800
I'm taking it.

32
00:02:41,159 --> 00:02:41,680
My lord,

33
00:02:43,639 --> 00:02:45,879
I am a scholar from the seventh year of Rende.

34
00:02:46,879 --> 00:02:48,240
Though with the Imperial Inspectorate,

35
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,879
you cannot use unauthorized punishment.

36
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,520
You broke into my house without cause,

37
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:53,159
brutalizing my son. This is...

38
00:02:53,319 --> 00:02:55,000
You dare call yourself a scholar?

39
00:02:55,199 --> 00:02:56,360
As an educated man,

40
00:02:56,599 --> 00:02:57,759
is this how you raised your son?

41
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:01,360
What on earth happened here?

42
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:07,560
My lord,

43
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,639
the person you're looking for,

44
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:09,800
two hours ago,

45
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,039
said there was an emergency at home,

46
00:03:11,159 --> 00:03:13,000
and has already left the residence.

47
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:13,919
You're lying!

48
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,960
My sister never came home at all.

49
00:03:17,319 --> 00:03:19,560
Dare to deceive the Imperial Inspectorate?

50
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,000
If you don't believe me, my lord,

51
00:03:21,159 --> 00:03:22,560
feel free to search the Hu residence.

52
00:03:22,919 --> 00:03:24,479
Trying to stall for time, are you?

53
00:03:28,479 --> 00:03:29,360
Stop!

54
00:03:29,719 --> 00:03:30,479
You madman!

55
00:03:30,639 --> 00:03:31,719
Father, save me!

56
00:03:31,919 --> 00:03:32,680
Save me!

57
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,759
Not afraid I'll appeal to the Emperor?

58
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,360
No one's stopping you.

59
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:39,120
But are you even worthy?

60
00:03:40,039 --> 00:03:41,319
I'll ask one more time.

61
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:43,960
Where is Xiao Mei?

62
00:03:45,319 --> 00:03:47,319
She's, she's, she's...

63
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:49,120
in the well, in the well!

64
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:50,800
In the well, in the well!

65
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:52,800
Take me there, now!

66
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:54,000
Hurry, take him there!

67
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:05,039
Sis!

68
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:07,199
Sis, you can't die on me, sis!

69
00:04:08,159 --> 00:04:09,120
Sis!

70
00:04:09,919 --> 00:04:10,400
This...

71
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,039
This isn't my fault.

72
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,439
She was too headstrong.

73
00:04:13,719 --> 00:04:15,000
She brought it on herself.

74
00:04:21,199 --> 00:04:22,279
My son!

75
00:04:24,199 --> 00:04:25,959
Master, Master, Master!

76
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,160
The Master has fainted!

77
00:04:27,319 --> 00:04:27,920
Are you all right, Master?

78
00:04:28,199 --> 00:04:28,959
Are you all right, Master?

79
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,279
Sis!

80
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:46,639
Sis!

81
00:05:26,759 --> 00:05:27,279
She can still be saved.

82
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:25,319
Xiao Mei!

83
00:06:26,279 --> 00:06:26,759
Wake up!

84
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:28,519
Xiao Mei!

85
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:37,920
Xiao Mei!

86
00:06:41,839 --> 00:06:42,399
Master.

87
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,120
Is it really you?

88
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:47,879
It's me.

89
00:06:49,399 --> 00:06:50,040
Thank goodness.

90
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:51,879
I thought

91
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:54,000
I'd never see you again.

92
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:58,240
Sis!

93
00:06:58,759 --> 00:06:59,480
What happened?

94
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:00,519
She's fine.

95
00:07:01,399 --> 00:07:02,240
She just passed out.

96
00:07:12,399 --> 00:07:13,079
Take this.

97
00:07:14,439 --> 00:07:15,720
Take good care of Xiao Mei for now.

98
00:07:16,079 --> 00:07:16,680
Master Ning.

99
00:07:16,959 --> 00:07:18,519
This is too precious. I can't accept it.

100
00:07:19,199 --> 00:07:20,319
Just take it when I tell you to.

101
00:07:27,519 --> 00:07:28,079
Xiao Mei.

102
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,480
I have to go on a long journey.

103
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,519
I might not be back for a long time.

104
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:41,000
You must take good care of yourself.

105
00:07:44,839 --> 00:07:45,800
Imperial Inspectorate, official business!

106
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:46,800
Seal off the Hu residence.

107
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:47,800
My lord!

108
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,399
Ning, are you all right?

109
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:01,040
Are you okay?

110
00:08:02,759 --> 00:08:03,519
What are you doing here?

111
00:08:03,839 --> 00:08:04,680
You've got the nerve to ask.

112
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:06,000
We were living it up at the Music Bureau.

113
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:06,959
Yudie told me you were in trouble.

114
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:07,519
Good lord.

115
00:08:07,639 --> 00:08:08,639
Didn't even have time to put my pants on.

116
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:10,279
Ran to the Imperial Inspectorate for help.

117
00:08:10,839 --> 00:08:12,399
Ning Chen, what's the matter with you?

118
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,120
First you killed the royal brother-in-law,

119
00:08:14,319 --> 00:08:15,439
and now you storm a scholar's residence.

120
00:08:15,759 --> 00:08:16,439
Do you have any idea?

121
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,839
He holds an official scholarly rank.

122
00:08:18,079 --> 00:08:18,680
Even if he were guilty,

123
00:08:18,839 --> 00:08:20,399
he must be sentenced before punishment.

124
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:21,600
Using private punishment like this,

125
00:08:21,759 --> 00:08:23,000
if those treacherous officials find out,

126
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:25,000
they'll surely impeach you to the Emperor.

127
00:08:25,399 --> 00:08:27,120
Ning, can you stop being so reckless?

128
00:08:27,279 --> 00:08:28,639
Follow some rules, would you?

129
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:30,759
Rules?

130
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:33,399
Reckless?

131
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:36,559
If the one lying here today

132
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,600
were your own family,

133
00:08:38,879 --> 00:08:40,159
would you still stand here

134
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:42,240
lecturing me about principles?

135
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:47,600
Xiao Mei may be a humble nobody,

136
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:51,440
but she treats me best in this world.

137
00:08:53,799 --> 00:08:55,440
When I used to get bullied,

138
00:08:56,879 --> 00:08:58,559
she always stood in front to protect me.

139
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,639
When I was starving,

140
00:09:02,399 --> 00:09:03,919
she always shared the food

141
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:04,639
from her own bowl with me.

142
00:09:06,559 --> 00:09:07,840
When I was sick,

143
00:09:09,279 --> 00:09:11,320
she stayed up all night by my side,

144
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:12,600
taking care of me.

145
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:16,519
So...

146
00:09:16,679 --> 00:09:17,159
Sister,

147
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:18,519
if the law won't protect you,

148
00:09:19,559 --> 00:09:20,360
I will.

149
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:22,519
If this world

150
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:24,960
is destined to be shrouded in darkness,

151
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:28,039
then I'll be the blade

152
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,960
that cuts through the darkness.

153
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,120
Hu Qiang

154
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:40,919
got what he deserved.

155
00:09:41,600 --> 00:09:43,360
Silver-Robed Ning upheld the law fairly.

156
00:09:44,519 --> 00:09:46,000
Hu Maode failed to raise his son properly.

157
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:47,399
Demoted to commoner.

158
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:49,559
His Majesty is wise indeed.

159
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:52,120
Next time I see the old man,

160
00:09:52,639 --> 00:09:53,879
I've got to kowtow to him.

161
00:09:54,919 --> 00:09:55,480
Ning,

162
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:58,000
what's your relationship with His Majesty?

163
00:09:58,399 --> 00:09:59,039
Yeah.

164
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:03,240
Let's just say it's quite extraordinary.

165
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:05,879
Practically like father and son.

166
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:07,799
Could it be...

167
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:10,360
an illegitimate son?

168
00:10:14,919 --> 00:10:15,440
Don't talk nonsense.

169
00:10:16,399 --> 00:10:17,240
What rubbish.

170
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:23,720
Ning Chen killing Hu Qiang

171
00:10:23,879 --> 00:10:25,000
was justified.

172
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:26,919
But now we need a way out

173
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:28,759
to silence the wagging tongues.

174
00:10:29,679 --> 00:10:31,159
The front lines are dangerous,

175
00:10:31,399 --> 00:10:33,440
but if Ning Chen can return alive,

176
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:35,320
then he'll have earned military merit.

177
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:36,879
But, Father,

178
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,120
once he reaches the border...

179
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:40,360
Guards!

180
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:41,919
Lord Chancellor.

181
00:10:42,399 --> 00:10:43,559
Do as I told you before.

182
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:45,080
Yes.

183
00:10:48,879 --> 00:10:49,320
Grandfather,

184
00:10:49,679 --> 00:10:50,360
what are you trying to do?

185
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:57,039
If only you three brothers had any spine,

186
00:10:57,879 --> 00:10:59,279
why would I have to

187
00:10:59,759 --> 00:11:01,559
stoop to acting against a youngster?

188
00:11:22,519 --> 00:11:23,360
Candied hawthorns!

189
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:24,600
Candied hawthorns!

190
00:11:25,639 --> 00:11:26,120
Want one?

191
00:11:26,799 --> 00:11:27,440
How much, sir?

192
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:28,039
Two coppers.

193
00:11:28,159 --> 00:11:28,559
Here.

194
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:30,320
Thank you, sir.

195
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:31,840
You're welcome.

196
00:11:32,919 --> 00:11:33,919
This one looks pretty good.

197
00:11:34,039 --> 00:11:34,519
You have it first.

198
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,360
Candied hawthorns!

199
00:11:37,519 --> 00:11:39,000
Candied hawthorns!

200
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:39,759
Is it good?

201
00:11:40,759 --> 00:11:42,840
Candied hawthorns!

202
00:11:56,559 --> 00:11:57,000
Move!

203
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:00,120
Out of the way!

204
00:12:00,679 --> 00:12:01,200
Move aside!

205
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:03,799
Out of the way!

206
00:12:06,519 --> 00:12:07,279
Move aside!

207
00:12:10,759 --> 00:12:11,360
Are you all right?

208
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:12,759
I'm fine.

209
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:13,480
What about you?

210
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:42,440
Seize him at once!

211
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:55,679
Ning Chen is a good man!

212
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:57,320
A good man?

213
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,360
He's a lackey of the court.

214
00:12:59,879 --> 00:13:01,720
He kills the innocent without a care.

215
00:13:01,919 --> 00:13:02,679
His crimes are countless.

216
00:13:03,399 --> 00:13:05,200
Ten deaths wouldn't pay for them.

217
00:13:05,559 --> 00:13:06,200
That's a lie!

218
00:13:07,279 --> 00:13:08,679
For the people of Chongzhou,

219
00:13:09,279 --> 00:13:10,639
Ning Chen risked his own head

220
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:11,799
to slay the Emperor's brother-in-law.

221
00:13:11,919 --> 00:13:13,399
Everyone praises him as a hero.

222
00:13:13,879 --> 00:13:14,799
Enough talk.

223
00:13:15,759 --> 00:13:17,240
Today, I'll grant your wish.

224
00:13:17,519 --> 00:13:19,120
Die together as star-crossed lovers.

225
00:13:29,039 --> 00:13:29,519
Retreat!

226
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:33,720
Don't move.

227
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:35,639
Ning Chen!

228
00:13:36,279 --> 00:13:36,799
Are you all right?

229
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:40,559
I'm fine.

230
00:13:42,159 --> 00:13:43,120
Take him back to the Imperial Inspectorate.

231
00:13:43,919 --> 00:13:44,799
Interrogate him thoroughly.

232
00:13:45,240 --> 00:13:45,720
Yes, sir.

233
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:46,960
Move!

234
00:13:48,440 --> 00:13:50,039
My dear Ning, you're hurt.

235
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:51,519
Let me take you to a physician.

236
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:54,000
Yudie.

237
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:56,559
Do you know how dangerous that was?

238
00:13:57,240 --> 00:13:58,120
Why didn't you run away?

239
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:00,879
Wherever you are,

240
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:02,559
that's where I'll be.

